    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">0</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">4</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">0</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">3</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">59.3</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">72.0</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">52.0</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">0</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">1</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">0</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">0</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">0.0000</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">119</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">1018</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Monzó-Nebot, Esther</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">The proposal effectively identifies a widespread issue in the reliance on monocentric approaches to Spanish language teaching. It suggests leveraging Spain&#039;s substantial economic investment in Spanish education while integrating artificial intelligence to enhance training in Latin American Spanish (minoritized in Spanish-language standardization) to meet China’s market needs.</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">The proposal effectively identifies a widespread issue in the reliance on monocentric approaches to Spanish language teaching. It suggests leveraging Spain&#039;s substantial economic investment in Spanish education while integrating artificial intelligence to enhance training in Latin American Spanish to meet China’s market needs.&#10;While this reviewer acknowledges the commendable nature of the initiative, several methodological concerns need to be addressed for the abstract to adequately shape the expectations of conference attendees. The methodology is currently described in vague terms, mentioning the application of &quot;ChatGPT&quot; with &quot;prompt engineering&quot; without sufficient detail. More comprehensive explanations of the methodology would be beneficial. Additionally, caution is recommended regarding the known biases and inaccuracies of ChatGPT. It is important to clarify how the initiative plans to manage the confidently presented mistakes ChatGPT is known for, ensuring students can distinguish between accurate and inaccurate information. Furthermore, it is crucial to address how the proposal will manage the issue of anglicisms that ChatGPT may introduce due to its training corpora and algorithms.&#10;In summary, the proposal is intriguing, but providing further details (especially complementary methods, including human supervision or reference materials) would greatly enhance the assessment of its value.&#10;</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">52</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">1297</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Martínez Nieto, Roxana Beatriz</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">El artículo propone el uso de la IA, exactamente el empleo de ChatGPT para avanzar en el conocimiento del español como lengua extranjera dirigido a estudiantes chinos. La clave de la contribución se halla en discernir entre la enseñanza de español de España, i. e., castellano, y espñol america, i.e. el que se habla en latinoamérica. A través de la comprensión de la diversidad lingüística del español se persigue mejorar el intercambio cultural y la cooperación multidisciplinar entre China y los países latinoamericanos.</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Me complace brindar una evaluación positiva para la presente contribución. &#10;&#10;Una de las fortalezas del trabajo radica en su enfoque sistemático para realizar una investigación precisa y detallada sobre los problemas a los que se enfrentan los estudiantes chinos durante su aprendizaje del español como lengua extranjera y que son abordados a través de herramientas digitales como la IA y el empleo del ChatGPT.&#10;&#10;El estudio demuestra el impacto tangible de estos enfoques digitales dentro de la disciplina lingüística y su repercusión en cooperación multidisciplinar entre China y los países latinoamericanos&#10;&#10;Una muestra de debilidad puede hallarse en la falta de desarrollo metodológico de las herramientas digitales a disposición de los docentes que imparten español como lengua extranjera para sinohablantes, así como un análisis de de caso en avances recientes y tendencias emergentes en este tipo de enseñanza.</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">La contribución es merecedora de ser publicada y puede revertir en una mejora de la enseñanza de ELE en China, si bien la metodología de enseñanza debe quedar muy clara para los docentes. </ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">72</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">1250</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Gauthereau, Lorena</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">This presentation focuses on the use of ChatGPT/AI in teaching Spanish-language acquisition in China. This seeks to fill a gap between a curriculum that is primarily focused on Peninsular Spanish and the need to learn Latin American and US Latino Spanish. </ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">The use of AI in the language classroom is an interesting topic that would be useful to explore during the conference. I think it&#039;s also great that they identified that students need to be exposed to these different registers of regional Spanish because it will help them in their careers. &#10;&#10;In order to strengthen the proposal, I would suggest citing scholarship about AI pedagogy as well as work on Spanish-language teaching models. In addition, the authors can clarify the following: How will the students interact with the ChatGPT materials? How will the authenticity of the language in AI texts be checked? Can the authors explain why they suggest this model as opposed to using original texts from Latin American/the United States? Are there any specific methodological approaches being taken? </ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">54</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="Number">-1</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Rejected</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s22"><Data ss:Type="DateTime">2024-09-07T17:05:18.000</Data></Cell>
