    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">We tried to select the fields this most closely fits but some of the choices may not be entirely satisfactory. We anticipate this paper will be more about the state of DH as a mode of professionalization and training for students.</ss:Data></Cell>
