    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Dear Sir/Ma&#039;am,&#10;I am a doctoral scholar, currently in my first year of pursuing PhD in English. My research centers on hashtag narratives and I wish to participate in this conference to learn more about Digital Humanities and its discourse in the present arena of studies. I hope you will give me a chance to present my work and gain meaningful insights. </ss:Data></Cell>
