    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Grumbach, Liz</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Wermer-Colan, Henry Alexander (Temple University)</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Dear Program Committee and Chairs, &#10;I&#039;m pleased to submit an abstract for a research project I&#039;m currently working on about the impact of misinformation during the flooding in the South of Brazil.&#10;I’ve already had some preliminary results, and I&#039;m expecting to finish this project in the first week of July. &#10;I&#039;d love to share the results during the conference.&#10;&#10;Best regards,&#10;&#10;Livia</ss:Data></Cell>
