    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Given your conference’s commitment to cross-disciplinary engagement, I want to add to my submission that I have a background in Information Technology. I have worked as an IT professional since 2019, and my approach towards the subject of my presentation will reflect my hands-on experience working with technology. For a summary of my professional qualifications, please refer to my LinkedIn page: https://www.linkedin.com/in/laszlotaba/</ss:Data></Cell>
