    <Cell ss:StyleID="s22"><Data ss:Type="DateTime">2024-11-08T10:30:00.000</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s22"><Data ss:Type="DateTime">2024-11-08T11:45:00.000</Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Sadler, Jesse Robert (Virginia Tech)</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">O&#039;Neil, Erica (Arizona State University)</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">I recently graduated from Brandeis University with a BA in Computer Science and an interdisciplinary major in Technology and Culture, focused on applying anthropological lenses to techno-social phenomena. I’ve been looking to apply those skills to some formalized research, and this topic has so much potential. I’m passionate about understanding these communities better, and am excited to learn more about how they work. Thank you for considering this submission!</ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
