    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String"></ss:Data></Cell>
    <Cell><ss:Data ss:Type="String">Note 1: we will be presenting a substantive draft of this minor, and will be welcoming suggestions and questions form other participants,&#10;Note 2: depending on their teaching schedule, only a subset of the many authors listed above might participate.</ss:Data></Cell>
